<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>폼 전송 결과</title>
    <style>
      span {
        color: coral;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%= title %> 폼 결과 확인하기</h1>
    <div><span><%= userInfo.name %></span>님 환영합니다!</div>
    <div>성별은 <span> <%= userInfo.gender%></span>이고,</div>
    <div>
      생년월일은 <span><%=userInfo.year%></span>년
      <span><%=userInfo.month%></span>월 <span><%=userInfo.day%></span>일이네요.
    </div>
    <div>취미는 <span><%=userInfo.interest%></span>이네요.</div>
    <div>좋아하는 색상은 <span><%=userInfo.color%></span></div>
    이군요! <% console.log(title, userInfo)%>
  </body>
</html>
